          <h2>Purpose</h2>
          <p class="lead">This Project Aims to Connect Students in My Schol with Their Favorite Vendors/Food Seller in the School without the stress of taking a shuttle down to the shopping complex or working down and all those stress, so you just seat whereever you are and make the order and it just get's delivered to you directly at your Department.</p>
         
