        <!-- HTML Structure
		============================ -->
        <section id="idocs_html_structure">
          <h2>Scope</h2>
          <p>This Platform Includes:<br>
              <ol>
            <li>Vendor Registration, which securely registers vendors and authenticate them.</li>
            <li>User Registration, which  securely registers Users and authenticate them
            </li>
            <li>Digital Wallet, a Digital Wallet that allows Users to fund and Securely Make transactions with their wallet Balance. Also Allowing Vendors to securely accumulate sales and request for Withdrawal</li>
            <li>Food Listing, a very easy to use interface for vendor's to list foods for sale on their pages</li>
            
            <li>Food Ordering, allowing Registered Users to Add Food to their Cart and Check them Out</li>
            <li>Payment Processing, crediting vendor for orders and debiting users for order, also Keeping a Track of Payment/Transactions History</li>

          </ol>

          <p class="alert alert-danger">Note: Users can check out Orders from Only One Vendor at a Time, this is to make sorting and fund splitting fast and easy. </p>
        </section>
        
		<hr class="divider">
		        
